Deptel 521,.June 24; Embtel 6, July 4;
                        Embtel 14, July 9, 1959;Embdespatches: No. 624, May 13; No. 669, May 25; No.
                        667, May 29;No. 677, June 4; and No. 726, June 24, 1959.None printed; these telegrams and despatches dealt
                            with the revision of the U.S. aid program and with Marroquin’s attacks
                            on the program. The respective file numbers are 814.00–TA/6–2459;
                            814.00–TA/7–459; 814.00–TA/7–959; 714.00/-5–1359; 714.5–MSP/5–2559;
                            714.00(W)/5–959; 714.5–MSP/6–2459; 814.00–TA/7–959.
